  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Why did Elizabeth tell Nigel that she was going to the dentist?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "伊丽莎白为什么告诉奈杰尔她要去看牙医？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "I crossed the street to avoid meeting him, but he saw me and came running towards me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我穿过马路想避开他，可他看见了我，朝我跑了过来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "It was no use pretending that I had not seen him, so I waved to him.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "假装没看见他已经没有用了，于是我向他挥了挥手。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "I never enjoy meeting Nigel Dykes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我从来都不喜欢遇见奈杰尔·戴克斯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "He never has anything to do.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他总是无所事事。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "No matter how busy you are, he always insists on coming with you.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不管你多忙，他总是坚持要跟着你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "I had to think of a way of preventing him from following me around all morning.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我只得想个办法，不让他整个上午都跟着我到处走。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Hello, Nigel, I said.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你好，奈杰尔。”我说道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Fancy meeting you here.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "真巧在这里遇见你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Hi, Elizabeth, Nigel answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你好，伊丽莎白。”奈杰尔回答道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I was just wondering how to spend the morning.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我刚才还在琢磨上午怎么打发呢。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Until I saw you.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“直到我看见了你。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "You're not busy doing anything, are you?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你现在没忙什么吧？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "No, not at all, I answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“一点也不忙。”我回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "I'm going to.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我正要去……”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Would you mind my coming with you?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你不介意我跟你一起去吧？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "He asked before I had finished speaking.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我还没说完，他就问道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Not at all, I lied.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“一点也不介意。”我撒谎说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "But I'm going to the dentist.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“不过我是去看牙医。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "Then I'll come with you, he answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“那我就跟你一起去。”他回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "There's always plenty to read in the waiting room.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“候诊室里总有很多东西可以看。”"
      }
    }
  ],
